thread.title: Colorado Springs I-25 crash leaves one dead, two injured
thread.title_full: Colorado Springs I-25 crash leaves one dead, two injured - The Denver Post

author: Jesse Paul
title: Colorado Springs I-25 crash leaves one dead, two injured
text:
One person was killed and two others injured Monday night in a single-vehicle crash on Interstate 25 in Colorado Springs.
The Colorado State Patrol says the crash happened in the interstate's southbound lanes near the Interquest Parkway exit.
A photo from the scene showed a badly mangled vehicle.
Further details in the crash were not immediately released.
